modules.description: Provides functions to share text, images, and links via native social media interfaces on mobile devices. Operates on strings, file paths, and URLs to enable seamless integration with device-specific sharing capabilities. Enables users to trigger system-level sharing dialogs with predefined content and metadata.

Creates and manages sharing configurations with customizable message, subject, files, and URL parameters. Handles result validation and app-specific feedback from social media sharing actions. Enables direct sharing to platforms like Twitter, Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp, and SMS with platform-specific options and callback handling.
